<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 27, 1994, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 2; Column 1; Advance Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1759 words 
</P>
