Traffic and transportation 22% 8% Job opportunities 18% 50% * 
</P>
<P>
 Community Images 
</P>
<P>
 Virtually no one living in the new suburbs takes issue with the idea that 
their communities are good places to raise children; nine in 10 agree that it 
is distinct from the rest of the county and generally safe from crime and 
gangs. The feeling they live in a child-friendly place is much stronger in the 
southern foothills specifically than in either South County generally or North 
County: 
</P>
<P>
