<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 27, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
