COMMUNITY NEWS: PLAYA DEL REY; U.S. OFFICIAL TO INSPECT BALLONA WETLANDS, OPEN 
AREAS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By SUSAN WOODWARD 
</P>
