<TEXT>
<P>
 Assistant Secretary of the Interior George Frampton will tour the Ballona 
Wetlands during a visit to the region next month. 
</P>
<P>
 Frampton, accompanied by Rep. Jane Harman (D-Marina del Rey), will tour 
several open areas in the South Bay on April 6 as well as the wetlands. 
