<TEXT>
<P>
 Actors' pay -- Actors in the L.A. Theatre Works' "The Play's the Thing" radio 
revival series receive a standard contract fee in accordance with the American 
Federation of Television and Radio Artists. A Westside story Thursday reported 
that they are not paid. 
